wylbur an interactive text editing and remote job entry system wylbur is a comprehensive system for manipulating all kinds of text such as computer programs  letters and manuscripts using typewriter terminals connected to a computer  it has facilities for  remote job entry and retrieval as well as facilities for text alignment and justification  a powerful  method for addressing text by content is provided  this paper describes the external appearance of wylbur  as well as its internal structure  a short description of the major features of orvyl a general purpose  timesharing system which operates in conjunction with wylbur is also included cacm may 1973 fajman r borgelt j 